title: A1534 820-00687-A
message:
Hello,

I have an A1534 820-00687-A that has no power. It pulls 19.5V from ampmeter, but 0Amp.

I have 8.6V on PPBUS_G3H, but PPVIN_G3H_P3V3G3H is 20V, Is that normal value?

title: A1534 820-00687-A
message:
Voltages look good.
You should check voltage on all big coils.

Any history available?
At least 3V3_S5 appears?

Be aware, like all A1534 boards, CPU will fail soon; if is not dead already...

title: A1534 820-00687-A
message:
Use 820-00244 schematic; original not available.

You can't get L7430 voltage.
Please, post accurate information.

"PP3V3_S5 = 3.3V"
Did you check it at L7690?

Check if 3V3_SUS comes high.

title: A1534 820-00687-A
message:

title: A1534 820-00687-A
message: Check S5_PWRGD, PM_BATLOW_L and PCH's RTC signals.

title: A1534 820-00687-A
message:

title: A1534 820-00687-A
message:
